-- Studio-only build: no executor functions (getconnections / readfile /
-- writefile / setclipboard). Keybind is in-memory, the notification and
-- confirmation popups are self-contained, and auto-accept uses Roblox's
-- VirtualInputManager (works in Studio play-tests only).
--====================================================================

